The Israel Defense Forces provides an account of five months of limited war in the northern theater (Lebanon and Syria) of hostilities:

- more than 1,200 air strikes;
- more than 3,100 ground strokes;
- more than 300 militants were eliminated;
- more than 750 militants were injured.

The army emphasizes that it will continue to carry out strikes and act in order to minimize Hezbollah's combat potential in Lebanon.@yigal_levin
